Dialogue: 0,00:00:01.97,00:00:09.99,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:00:09.99,00:00:16.00,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ ひからびた言葉をつないで
Dialogue: 0,00:00:16.00,00:00:20.51,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ それでも僕等シンプルな
Dialogue: 0,00:00:20.51,00:00:24.52,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ 想いを伝えたいだけなの
Dialogue: 0,00:00:24.52,00:00:30.53,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ 吹き抜けるくすんだあの日の風は
Dialogue: 0,00:00:30.53,00:00:35.04,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ 昨日の廃虚に打ち捨てて
Dialogue: 0,00:00:35.04,00:00:40.05,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ 君と笑う 今を生きるのだ
Dialogue: 0,00:00:40.05,00:00:44.56,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ それでもあの出来事が
Dialogue: 0,00:00:44.56,00:00:49.07,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ 君を苦しめるだろ？
Dialogue: 0,00:00:49.07,00:00:52.58,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ だからこそサヨナラなんだ
Dialogue: 0,00:00:52.58,00:00:56.02,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ このまま何も残らずに
Dialogue: 0,00:00:56.02,00:00:59.52,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ あなたと分かち合うだけ
Dialogue: 0,00:00:59.52,00:01:02.53,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ やがて僕等は
Dialogue: 0,00:01:02.53,00:01:06.54,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ それが全てだと気がついて
Dialogue: 0,00:01:06.54,00:01:10.04,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ 悲しみは頬を伝って
Dialogue: 0,00:01:10.04,00:01:13.55,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ 涙の河になるだけ
Dialogue: 0,00:01:13.55,00:01:19.56,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ 揺れる想いは強い渦になって
Dialogue: 0,00:01:19.56,00:01:24.07,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ 溶け合うのよ
Dialogue: 0,00:01:31.04,00:01:35.05,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ﾁｮｳｼﾞ)《シカマルは ずっと僕のことを信じてくれてた！》
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.21,0:01:35.46,Italics,,0,0,0,,O Shikamaru sempre\Nacreditou em mim.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:35.05,00:01:39.06,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｼｶﾏﾙ)俺やネジ ここにいる誰よりも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.81,0:01:39.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Sei mais do que o Neji,\Nmais do que todos aqui...
Dialogue: 0,00:01:39.06,00:01:41.06,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,あいつは強い｡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.42,0:01:41.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele é o mais forte entre nós.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:41.06,00:01:46.07,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:01:46.07,00:01:48.58,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ﾁｮｳｼﾞ)行くぞ デブ！(次郎坊)くっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.49,0:01:47.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos, gordão!
Dialogue: 0,00:01:48.58,00:01:51.01,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,てめぇが言うな！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.23,0:01:50.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Não se atreva a falar isso!
Dialogue: 0,00:01:51.01,00:01:54.52,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ﾁｮｳｼﾞ)部分倍化の術！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.31,0:01:53.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Jutsu de Expansão Parcial...
Dialogue: 0,00:01:54.52,00:01:57.53,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,腕！(次郎坊)ん!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.37,0:01:56.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Braço!
Dialogue: 0,00:01:57.53,00:01:59.53,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,うわっ！
Dialogue: 0,00:01:59.53,00:02:02.54,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:02:02.54,00:02:06.04,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,部分倍化の術…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.85,0:02:05.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Jutsu de Expansão Parcial...
Dialogue: 0,00:02:06.04,00:02:08.55,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(次郎坊)くっ…｡(ﾁｮｳｼﾞ)足！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.99,0:02:08.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Perna!
Dialogue: 0,00:02:08.55,00:02:10.55,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,部分倍化の術
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.25,0:02:10.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Jutsu de Expansão Parcial...
Dialogue: 0,00:02:10.55,00:02:13.56,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,腕！(次郎坊)うっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.02,0:02:11.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Braço!
Dialogue: 0,00:02:13.56,00:02:23.57,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:02:25.58,00:02:29.09,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(次郎坊)ふざけるな カスが～！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.21,0:02:29.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Não mexa comigo, lixo!
Dialogue: 0,00:02:29.09,00:02:32.10,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:02:32.10,00:02:34.10,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,食らえ！(次郎坊)何!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.64,0:02:33.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Tome essa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.55,0:02:34.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Quê?!
Dialogue: 0,00:02:34.10,00:02:37.10,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,超倍化の術‼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.25,0:02:37.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Jutsu de Superexpansão!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.83,0:02:54.84,Title,,0,0,0,,Adeus, velho amigo!\N\NSempre acreditei em você!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.22,0:02:53.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Adeus, velho amigo!\NSempre acreditei em você!
Dialogue: 0,00:02:57.58,00:03:00.58,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ﾁｮｳｼﾞ)《やったよ シカマル…》
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.23,0:03:01.27,Italics,,0,0,0,,Eu consegui, Shikamaru...
Dialogue: 0,00:03:05.10,00:03:07.10,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ﾁｮｳｼﾞ)《何!?》
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.25,0:03:06.21,Italics,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,00:03:10.61,00:03:12.61,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(次郎坊)こんなヤツを相手に
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.68,0:03:13.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Não acredito que\Nprecisei ir ao estágio dois.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:12.61,00:03:16.11,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,状態２になるとはな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.39,0:03:16.28,Main,,0,0,0,,contra um oponente como esse.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:19.63,00:03:21.63,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(次郎坊) 昇撃掌！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.06,0:03:22.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Palma Estilhaçar!
Dialogue: 0,00:03:21.63,00:03:23.63,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ﾁｮｳｼﾞ)うわっ！
Dialogue: 0,00:03:23.63,00:03:31.15,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:03:31.15,00:03:33.15,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,うっ！
Dialogue: 0,00:03:33.15,00:03:41.67,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.62,0:03:44.65,Italics,,0,0,0,,Que aparência é essa?
Dialogue: 0,00:03:41.67,00:03:44.68,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ﾁｮｳｼﾞ)《何だ？ あの姿は…》
Dialogue: 0,00:03:44.68,00:03:47.68,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(次郎坊)こうなったら終わりだ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.17,0:03:47.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Agora que usei isso, já era.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.92,0:03:52.12,Main,,0,0,0,,No estágio dois, consigo usar um poder dez\Nvezes mais forte do que eu estava usando.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.12,0:03:53.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Sou invencível.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.79,0:04:04.89,Italics,,0,0,0,,Sinto muita dor para me mexer...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.89,0:04:08.51,Italics,,0,0,0,,Quem imaginaria que os efeitos da pílula\Nde curry seriam tão intensos?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.98,0:04:15.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Isso é o que acontece
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.49,0:04:18.99,Main,,0,0,0,,com vermes insolentes\Nque se metem em tudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.46,0:04:27.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Brincar de ninja é mais a sua praia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.89,0:04:35.73,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Levante a mão se está\Nbrincando de ninja!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.13,0:04:39.63,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Esperem!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.63,0:04:41.97,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Pedra, papel ou tesoura!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.28,0:04:43.71,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Separar!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.07,0:04:47.48,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Um, dois, três...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.48,0:04:50.45,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Espera!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.92,0:04:57.26,Flashback,,0,0,0,,99... 100!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.22,0:05:05.33,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Ei, falei para sair!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.96,0:05:08.24,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Ai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.24,0:05:09.97,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Encontrei vocês!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.33,0:05:12.94,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Desistam logo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.38,0:05:22.13,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Finalmente pegamos eles!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.13,0:05:26.59,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Tô cansado disso! O time\Ncom o Choji sempre perde!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.91,0:05:29.28,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Foi mal...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.83,0:05:51.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Preciso de muito Chakra\Npara esse estágio dois.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.80,0:05:55.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu vou pegar todo o\NChakra que lhe sobrou.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.87,0:06:00.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Bom, vou fazer minha refeição.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.82,0:06:08.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Tem pouco...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.23,0:06:10.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Você está vazio!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.62,0:06:13.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu ainda não comi o bastante!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.47,0:06:32.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Falei que ainda\Nnão comi o bastante!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.81,0:06:35.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Ué...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.09,0:06:38.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Só uma...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.52,0:06:43.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Quando eu disse que\Nnão comi o bastante...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.59,0:06:51.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Como eu pensava, você é um lixo,\Nnada mais que um peão de sacrifício.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.53,0:06:57.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Morra, seu gordo ridículo e rejeitado.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.17,0:07:01.21,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Não vou deixar você brincar\Nde ninja com a gente!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.60,0:07:03.22,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Por quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.62,0:07:06.41,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Porque se você brincar, vamos perder.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.41,0:07:08.09,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Você é lento.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.56,0:07:14.67,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Sim, mas aí o número\Nde pessoas será ímpar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.67,0:07:18.16,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Shogi só é divertido porque\No número de peças é par.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.13,0:07:24.36,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Ter uma peça inútil é o\Nmesmo que não ter nenhuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.36,0:07:25.61,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Sim, isso mesmo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.58,0:07:31.35,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Vamos ficar com menos pessoas\Ne não estamos reclamando.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.35,0:07:32.74,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Rápido, vamos lá!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.74,0:07:35.55,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Se não tiver problema\Npor você, tudo bem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.55,0:07:37.15,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Certo, está decidido!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.15,0:07:38.99,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Conseguiremos vencer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.99,0:07:39.49,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.49,0:07:41.69,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Onde vamos nos esconder dessa vez?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.45,0:08:23.09,Flashback,,0,0,0,,E todo o clã Akimichi\Né burro e lento...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.09,0:08:25.43,Flashback,,0,0,0,,É o que todos dizem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.43,0:08:26.76,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Sério...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.43,0:08:36.15,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Mas Choji, você é um cara gentil,\Nmais do que todo mundo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.13,0:08:43.52,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Um dia, certamente, você fará amigos\Nque enxergam essa sua qualidade.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.11,0:08:48.99,Flashback,,0,0,0,,E então você deve valorizá-los...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.99,0:08:51.82,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Para ser uma amizade em\Nque um acredita no outro.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.72,0:08:59.47,Flashback Italics,,0,0,0,,Será que vou conseguir fazer\Namigos assim? Alguém como eu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.47,0:09:01.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Descanse em paz.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.53,0:09:03.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Você não é o único que vou matar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.59,0:09:06.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Depois de matá-lo,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.84,0:09:13.52,Main,,0,0,0,,vou pegar aqueles caras cruéis, baixos\Ne malvados que o usaram como sacrifício.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.41,0:09:24.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Porque ele prometeu...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.02,0:09:31.00,Flashback,,0,0,0,,É melhor nos alcançar, Choji.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:32.50,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Certo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.99,0:09:39.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele certamente vai derrotar\No oponente e nos alcançar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.23,0:09:40.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.97,0:09:44.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Isso mesmo. Ele consegue.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.95,0:09:49.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Certo, enquanto estou aqui...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.31,0:09:52.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu também...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.86,0:09:57.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Certo, pessoal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.62,0:10:00.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos recuperar o Sasuke\Nantes de o Choji chegar!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.15,0:10:03.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Espere!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.22,0:10:06.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Certo! Aqui vamos nós!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.80,0:10:21.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele está atrasado... O Jirobo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.45,0:10:24.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele é ganancioso e come demais.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.55,0:10:27.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Provavelmente está sugando\No Chakra até dos ossos deles.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.42,0:10:30.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Queria que ele tivesse\Ntrocado comigo logo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.38,0:10:39.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Aqui, eu vou devolver!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.22,0:10:43.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Bom, então...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.52,0:10:46.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Se eu ficar aqui, não\Nconseguirei chegar a eles.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.61,0:10:49.74,Main,,0,0,0,,É hora de acabarmos com isso.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.73,0:10:55.97,Italics,,0,0,0,,Sobrou a pílula de pimenta chili...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.97,0:11:02.75,Italics,,0,0,0,,Mas se eu tomá-la,\Nvou certamente morrer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.41,0:11:10.73,Italics,,0,0,0,,Não se atreva a morrer, Choji.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.16,0:11:18.81,Italics,,0,0,0,,Temos feito tudo juntos\Ndesde aquele dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.75,0:11:41.53,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Oh, é você.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.72,0:11:45.50,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Você... Você é...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.02,0:11:47.96,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Não está brincando de ninja?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.39,0:11:50.20,Flashback,,0,0,0,,É um saco, então saí.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.28,0:11:54.20,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Aliás, este é meu local especial.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.20,0:11:55.93,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Seu local especial?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.93,0:12:01.38,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Gosto de deitar aqui e\Nficar vendo as nuvens.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.14,0:12:05.28,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Você veio olhar as nuvens?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.44,0:12:08.79,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Posso sentar aqui?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.79,0:12:10.69,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Opa, pode sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.62,0:12:18.23,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Este é um lugar ótimo.\NDá para ver bem as nuvens!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.49,0:12:21.70,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.63,0:12:27.00,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Por que você não...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.00,0:12:28.01,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.50,0:12:33.87,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Quer relaxar e ver as nuvens comigo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.27,0:12:36.45,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Certo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.85,0:12:40.99,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Sabe, eu trouxe um lanchinho, quer?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.99,0:12:42.42,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Sim, seria ótimo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.45,0:12:46.59,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Obrigado.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.65,0:12:54.61,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Comer batatinhas e ver as\Nnuvens... Isso é incrível.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.61,0:12:55.57,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.89,0:13:03.62,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Meu nome é Shikamaru,\Nsou do clã Nara.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.62,0:13:05.51,Flashback,,0,0,0,,E você, como se chama?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.17,0:13:10.65,Flashback,,0,0,0,,É Choji! Akimichi Choji!\NSou do clã Akimichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.65,0:13:14.69,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Choji, é? Acho que vamos nos dar bem.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:17.16,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Eu também!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.92,0:13:31.80,Italics,,0,0,0,,E, daqui para frente, sempre\Nfaremos as coisas juntos.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.59,0:13:34.74,Italics,,0,0,0,,Choji!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.44,0:13:49.16,Italics,,0,0,0,,Shikamaru, foi mal... Não vou conseguir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.01,0:13:52.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Acabou.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.98,0:13:54.99,Italics,,0,0,0,,Mas esse cara...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.32,0:13:59.83,Italics,,0,0,0,,Preciso vencê-lo, mesmo\Nque isso custe minha vida.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.83,0:14:02.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Não importa o que você\Nfaça agora, é tarde demais!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.75,0:14:04.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Palma Estilhaçar!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.56,0:14:32.23,Italics,,0,0,0,,O que é isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.72,0:14:34.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.69,0:14:37.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Soco do Pedregulho!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.83,0:14:41.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Nada.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.76,0:14:46.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Estou 100 vezes mais forte do que antes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.51,0:14:56.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Dizem que comida pode ser uma razão\Npara pessoas odiarem muito alguém.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.93,0:15:03.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Este soco... foi por ter\Ncomido minha última batata.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.06,0:15:04.51,Italics,,0,0,0,,Não pode ser!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.51,0:15:08.03,Italics,,0,0,0,,Esse cara tem tanto Chakra\Nque seu corpo mudou!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.56,0:15:10.46,Main,,0,0,0,,E isso é...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.96,0:15:17.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Por me zoar e me chamar de\N"gordo" e "peão de sacrifício"!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.29,0:15:20.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas, acima de tudo,\No que não posso perdoar...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.14,0:15:27.35,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Certamente sofrerão com um\Nlíder tão idiota, seus vermes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.35,0:15:29.76,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Bom, vou matá-los, seus perdedores,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.76,0:15:35.69,Flashback Italics,,0,0,0,,antes que sofram mais nas mãos\Nde um líder incompetente como ele.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.32,0:15:40.30,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Deveria culpar seu líder idiota\Npor ter escolhido você.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.16,0:15:45.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Você insultou meu melhor amigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.83,0:15:51.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Mais do que me insultar ou qualquer coisa,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.85,0:15:55.25,Main,,0,0,0,,além de ter comido\Nminha última batatinha...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.68,0:15:58.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Não posso perdoá-lo por isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.57,0:16:03.79,Italics,,0,0,0,,Todo meu Chakra...\Npara a minha mão esquerda!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.79,0:16:05.69,Italics,,0,0,0,,Essa não!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.69,0:16:10.06,Italics,,0,0,0,,Esse golpe... é o mais\Nforte de toda minha vida!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.66,0:16:13.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Espere! Não tenha tanta pressa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.86,0:16:58.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu venci...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.13,0:17:02.21,Italics,,0,0,0,,Eu venci...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.79,0:17:27.91,Italics,,0,0,0,,Pessoal...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.71,0:18:13.97,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Mas Choji...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.97,0:18:17.62,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Mas Choji, você é um cara gentil,\Nmais do que todo mundo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.36,0:18:25.33,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Um dia, certamente, você fará amigos\Nque enxergam essa sua qualidade.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.95,0:18:31.31,Flashback,,0,0,0,,E então você deve valorizá-los...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.31,0:18:33.84,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Para ser uma amizade em\Nque um acredita no outro.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.11,0:18:54.02,Main,,0,0,0,,"Rápido, para este lado"... É do Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.78,0:18:57.76,Main,,0,0,0,,"Todos estão à sua espera. Kiba."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.19,0:19:01.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Shikamaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.77,0:19:17.92,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Ino... Shika... Cho!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.39,0:19:33.73,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Mesmo que sejam apenas batatas,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.73,0:19:37.06,Flashback,,0,0,0,,não vou deixar ninguém\Ncomer a última! Ninguém!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.76,0:19:42.40,Flashback,,0,0,0,,O Choji e eu nos esforçamos muito como um time, durante anos,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.40,0:19:45.11,Flashback,,0,0,0,,então conseguimos ter\Num bom entrosamento.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.44,0:19:54.15,Italics,,0,0,0,,Papai...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.54,0:19:58.92,Italics,,0,0,0,,Eu fiz muitos amigos...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.68,0:20:36.53,Main,,0,0,0,,O que houve?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.82,0:20:43.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Nada.
Dialogue: 0,null,null,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,倍以上の力を出せる状態２に敵はいない｡
Dialogue: 0,00:03:53.13,00:04:02.14,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:04:02.14,00:04:04.65,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ﾁｮｳｼﾞ)《痛くて動けない…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:04:04.65,00:04:08.16,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,カレー丸の副作用がこんなにキツいなんて…》
Dialogue: 0,00:04:08.16,00:04:10.66,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:04:10.66,00:04:15.67,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(次郎坊)力もないクズがしゃしゃり出てくるから
Dialogue: 0,00:04:15.67,00:04:18.68,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,こういうことになる！
Dialogue: 0,00:04:18.68,00:04:22.18,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:04:22.18,00:04:27.69,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,お前らには忍者ごっこぐらいが お似合いだ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:04:27.69,00:04:31.20,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,ハァ ハァ ハァ…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:04:31.20,00:04:35.21,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(男の子１)＜忍者ごっこするヤツこの指 止～まれ！＞
Dialogue: 0,00:04:35.21,00:04:37.21,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(男の子たち)＜やる！ やる！＞
Dialogue: 0,00:04:37.21,00:04:39.22,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ﾁｮｳｼﾞ)＜待って～！＞
Dialogue: 0,00:04:39.22,00:04:41.72,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(男の子たち)＜じゃんけんぽん！＞
Dialogue: 0,00:04:41.72,00:04:43.73,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(男の子２)＜散れ！＞
Dialogue: 0,00:04:43.73,00:04:47.23,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(男の子たち)＜１ ２ ３…＞
Dialogue: 0,00:04:47.23,00:04:50.24,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ﾁｮｳｼﾞ)＜ま… 待ってよ～！＞
Dialogue: 0,00:04:53.68,00:04:58.19,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(男の子たち)＜99 100｡
Dialogue: 0,00:04:58.19,00:05:00.19,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,ヘヘヘ！＞
Dialogue: 0,00:05:01.70,00:05:03.20,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜あっ…＞
Dialogue: 0,00:05:03.20,00:05:05.70,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(男の子２)＜こら 散れって言っただろ！＞
Dialogue: 0,00:05:05.70,00:05:07.71,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜うっ… 痛っ＞
Dialogue: 0,00:05:07.71,00:05:09.71,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(男の子３･男の子４)＜見～つけた！＞
Dialogue: 0,00:05:09.71,00:05:13.22,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(男の子３)＜２人ともおとなしく降参しろ！＞
Dialogue: 0,00:05:13.22,00:05:15.22,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(男の子２)＜チッ＞
Dialogue: 0,00:05:19.23,00:05:21.74,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(男の子４)＜や～っと捕まえたぜ＞
Dialogue: 0,00:05:21.74,00:05:27.25,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜やんなるぜ ﾁｮｳｼﾞが入ったﾁｰﾑが絶対 負けちゃうんだもんな＞
Dialogue: 0,00:05:27.25,00:05:29.75,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜ごめん…＞
Dialogue: 0,00:05:29.75,00:05:32.76,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,ハァ ハァ ハァ…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:05:32.76,00:05:39.27,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:05:39.27,00:05:40.77,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,フン｡
Dialogue: 0,00:05:40.77,00:05:43.28,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:05:43.28,00:05:45.28,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,ぐっ！
Dialogue: 0,00:05:45.28,00:05:47.79,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:05:47.79,00:05:51.23,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,この状態２は やたらとチャクラがいるんでな
Dialogue: 0,00:05:51.23,00:05:56.24,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,お前の残りのチャクラすべて食わせてもらう｡
Dialogue: 0,00:05:56.24,00:06:00.25,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,さてと 頂きますか｡
Dialogue: 0,00:06:00.25,00:06:04.76,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:06:04.76,00:06:07.76,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,フン もう大して吸い取れねえ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:06:07.76,00:06:10.27,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,スカスカだ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:06:10.27,00:06:13.27,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,全然 食い足りねえな！
Dialogue: 0,00:06:13.27,00:06:23.28,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:06:28.30,00:06:29.81,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ﾁｮｳｼﾞ)がっ！
Dialogue: 0,00:06:29.81,00:06:32.81,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(次郎坊)食い足りねえって言ってんだろうが！
Dialogue: 0,00:06:32.81,00:06:34.82,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,あ？
Dialogue: 0,00:06:34.82,00:06:38.82,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,何だ 最後の一口だけか｡
Dialogue: 0,00:06:38.82,00:06:42.83,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,まだ食い足りねえってのによ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:06:42.83,00:06:46.34,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:06:46.34,00:06:48.34,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,やっぱり てめぇは
Dialogue: 0,00:06:48.34,00:06:52.28,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,捨て駒扱いのカスだったな｡
Dialogue: 0,00:06:52.28,00:06:57.79,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,死ね 仲間外れのあわれなデブ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:06:57.79,00:07:01.30,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(男の子１)＜お前は忍者ごっこ入れてやんない＞
Dialogue: 0,00:07:01.30,00:07:03.30,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜どうして？＞
Dialogue: 0,00:07:03.30,00:07:05.81,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(男の子２)＜お前が入ると負けちまうだろうが！＞
Dialogue: 0,00:07:05.81,00:07:08.31,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(男の子３)＜お前 鈍感だもん＞
Dialogue: 0,00:07:10.32,00:07:14.33,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜けどよ それじゃ人数も合わねえだろ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:07:14.33,00:07:18.34,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,将棋だって 同じ数の駒があっからおもしれぇんだぞ＞
Dialogue: 0,00:07:18.34,00:07:20.34,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜あぁ…＞
Dialogue: 0,00:07:20.34,00:07:23.85,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(男の子２)＜役に立たない駒なんて初めっからないのと同じだろ？＞
Dialogue: 0,00:07:23.85,00:07:25.85,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(男の子１)＜そうだ そうだ＞
Dialogue: 0,00:07:28.36,00:07:32.36,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜こっちが少ない分には文句ないだろ？ 早くやろうぜ＞
Dialogue: 0,00:07:32.36,00:07:35.37,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(男の子４)＜そっちがいいんならそれで いいけどよ…＞
Dialogue: 0,00:07:35.37,00:07:38.88,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜よし 決まりだ！＞(男の子１)＜これで勝てるぞ＞
Dialogue: 0,00:07:38.88,00:07:41.38,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(男の子５)＜よし どこ隠れる？＞(男の子６)＜さっきの…＞
Dialogue: 0,00:07:41.38,00:07:51.39,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:07:55.34,00:07:56.85,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜あ？＞
Dialogue: 0,00:07:56.85,00:08:06.86,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:08:16.89,00:08:18.39,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:08:18.39,00:08:22.90,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ﾁｮｳｼﾞ)＜んでね 秋道一族はデブばっかで鈍感だって
Dialogue: 0,00:08:22.90,00:08:24.90,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,みんな そう言うんだ＞
Dialogue: 0,00:08:24.90,00:08:26.90,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ﾁｮｳｻﾞ)＜そうか＞
Dialogue: 0,00:08:29.91,00:08:32.42,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜でもな チョウジ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:08:32.42,00:08:37.93,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,誰よりも お前は優しいヤツだ＞(ﾁｮｳｼﾞ)＜ん？＞
Dialogue: 0,00:08:37.93,00:08:41.94,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜いつか お前のそういうところを見てくれる友達が
Dialogue: 0,00:08:41.94,00:08:44.94,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,きっと できる｡
Dialogue: 0,00:08:44.94,00:08:48.95,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,そしたら お前はその友達を何より大切にして
Dialogue: 0,00:08:48.95,00:08:51.95,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,信じ合える仲間になればいい＞
Dialogue: 0,00:08:53.39,00:08:55.90,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ﾁｮｳｼﾞ)《ホントに できるのかなぁ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:08:55.90,00:08:59.40,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,そんな仲間が この僕に…》
Dialogue: 0,00:08:59.40,00:09:01.41,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,安心しろ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:09:01.41,00:09:04.41,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,お前だけを食らうわけではない｡
Dialogue: 0,00:09:04.41,00:09:08.92,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,お前を殺したあとはお前を捨て駒扱いした
Dialogue: 0,00:09:08.92,00:09:13.43,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,薄情で薄汚い ほかのゲスどもも食らってやるよ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:09:19.95,00:09:23.45,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,あいつは 約束したからな｡
Dialogue: 0,00:09:27.96,00:09:30.97,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜絶対 後から追いつけよチョウジ＞
Dialogue: 0,00:09:30.97,00:09:32.97,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ﾁｮｳｼﾞ)＜うん！＞
Dialogue: 0,00:09:32.97,00:09:36.48,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,あいつは 敵を倒して
Dialogue: 0,00:09:36.48,00:09:39.99,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,絶対に俺たちを追ってくる｡
Dialogue: 0,00:09:39.99,00:09:42.49,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ﾅﾙﾄ)ああ｡(キバ)ヘッ そうだな｡
Dialogue: 0,00:09:42.49,00:09:44.49,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,あいつだってやりゃ できるヤツだ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:09:44.49,00:09:47.00,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(赤丸のほえ声)
Dialogue: 0,00:09:47.00,00:09:50.01,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,よし んじゃ ついでに…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:09:50.01,00:09:52.51,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,ヘヘッ 俺も｡
Dialogue: 0,00:09:52.51,00:09:56.02,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｸﾅｲで彫る音)
Dialogue: 0,00:09:56.02,00:09:59.02,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,いいか？ みんなチョウジが追いつく前に
Dialogue: 0,00:09:59.02,00:10:01.03,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,サスケを取り戻すぜ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:10:01.03,00:10:04.03,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,あ…｡お… 待てよ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:10:04.03,00:10:07.04,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,おっしゃ～ 行くぜ！
Dialogue: 0,00:10:18.09,00:10:21.59,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(左近)遅いな 次郎坊のヤツ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:10:21.59,00:10:24.10,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(多由也)意地汚ぇ大食らいだからな｡
Dialogue: 0,00:10:24.10,00:10:27.10,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,骨の髄までチャクラを搾り取る気だろうよ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:10:27.10,00:10:30.61,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(鬼童丸)いいかげん 代わってほしいぜよ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:10:36.12,00:10:39.13,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(次郎坊)ほら 返してやるよ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:10:41.57,00:10:46.08,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,さてと グズグズしてると追いつけなくなるな｡
Dialogue: 0,00:10:46.08,00:10:49.08,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,そろそろ とどめを刺すとするか｡
Dialogue: 0,00:10:49.08,00:10:51.08,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,がっ…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:10:52.59,00:10:55.60,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ﾁｮｳｼﾞ)《残るは 赤のトンガラシ丸…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:10:55.60,00:10:58.60,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,でも… あれをのんだら
Dialogue: 0,00:10:58.60,00:11:01.11,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,間違いなく…
Dialogue: 0,00:11:01.11,00:11:03.11,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,死ぬ…》
Dialogue: 0,00:11:03.11,00:11:07.12,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｸﾅｲで彫る音)
Dialogue: 0,00:11:07.12,00:11:10.62,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｼｶﾏﾙ)《絶対に死ぬんじゃねえぞチョウジ》
Dialogue: 0,00:11:14.63,00:11:18.64,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｼｶﾏﾙ)《あの日から 俺たちはずっと一緒に やってきたんだ》
Dialogue: 0,00:11:24.65,00:11:26.66,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜ん？＞
Dialogue: 0,00:11:39.18,00:11:41.62,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜あ？ お前…＞
Dialogue: 0,00:11:41.62,00:11:45.63,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜あ… 君は さっきの…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:11:45.63,00:11:48.13,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,忍者ごっこは？＞(ｼｶﾏﾙ)＜ヘッヘヘ…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:11:48.13,00:11:51.14,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,めんどくせぇから抜けてきた＞(ﾁｮｳｼﾞ)＜え？＞
Dialogue: 0,00:11:51.14,00:11:55.65,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜ちなみに その席は俺の特等席＞(ﾁｮｳｼﾞ)＜特等席？＞
Dialogue: 0,00:11:55.65,00:11:58.65,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜こ～んな天気のいい日はそこで あおむけになって
Dialogue: 0,00:11:58.65,00:12:02.66,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,雲 見んのが好きなんだよな 俺＞
Dialogue: 0,00:12:02.66,00:12:05.67,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜雲を見に来たの？＞
Dialogue: 0,00:12:05.67,00:12:08.67,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜そこ いいか？＞
Dialogue: 0,00:12:08.67,00:12:11.18,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜あっ うん…＞
Dialogue: 0,00:12:13.18,00:12:16.19,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｼｶﾏﾙ)＜ヘッヘヘ…やっぱ ここは いいよな｡
Dialogue: 0,00:12:16.19,00:12:18.19,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,よく雲が見える＞
Dialogue: 0,00:12:20.20,00:12:22.20,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ﾁｮｳｼﾞ)＜うん＞
Dialogue: 0,00:12:25.21,00:12:28.71,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｼｶﾏﾙ)＜お前も…＞(ﾁｮｳｼﾞ)＜え？＞
Dialogue: 0,00:12:28.71,00:12:31.22,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜俺と一緒に雲を見て
Dialogue: 0,00:12:31.22,00:12:34.73,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,のほほ～んと しようぜ＞
Dialogue: 0,00:12:34.73,00:12:36.73,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜うん｡
Dialogue: 0,00:12:36.73,00:12:40.67,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,そうだ 僕 お菓子持ってきてるんだ 一緒に食べよ＞
Dialogue: 0,00:12:40.67,00:12:44.68,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｼｶﾏﾙ)＜おっ いいね＞(ﾁｮｳｼﾞ)＜フフ… フフフ…＞
Dialogue: 0,00:12:44.68,00:12:47.18,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜サンキュー＞
Dialogue: 0,00:12:50.19,00:12:54.20,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜雲を見ながらポテチか最高だな＞
Dialogue: 0,00:12:54.20,00:12:55.70,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜うん！＞
Dialogue: 0,00:12:55.70,00:12:59.71,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ﾎﾟﾃﾄﾁｯﾌﾟｽを食べる音)
Dialogue: 0,00:12:59.71,00:13:03.22,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜俺はシカマルってんだ奈良一族の｡
Dialogue: 0,00:13:03.22,00:13:05.72,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,お前 名前は？＞
Dialogue: 0,00:13:05.72,00:13:10.23,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜チョウジ秋道一族の秋道チョウジ！＞
Dialogue: 0,00:13:10.23,00:13:15.24,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜チョウジかぁ…お前とは気が合いそうだぜ＞
Dialogue: 0,00:13:15.24,00:13:17.24,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜僕も＞
Dialogue: 0,00:13:17.24,00:13:26.76,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:13:26.76,00:13:28.77,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｼｶﾏﾙ)《これからも
Dialogue: 0,00:13:28.77,00:13:32.78,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,俺たちは ずっと一緒にやっていくんだからな｡
Dialogue: 0,00:13:32.78,00:13:35.78,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,チョウジ！》
Dialogue: 0,00:13:35.78,00:13:38.79,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(関節を鳴らす音)
Dialogue: 0,00:13:38.79,00:13:42.23,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ﾁｮｳｼﾞ)ハァ ハァ…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:13:42.23,00:13:44.23,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,ハァ…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:13:44.23,00:13:49.74,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ﾁｮｳｼﾞ)《シカマル…ごめん 僕 行けないや…》
Dialogue: 0,00:13:49.74,00:13:52.75,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,これで終わりだ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:13:52.75,00:13:55.76,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ﾁｮｳｼﾞ)《でも… こいつは
Dialogue: 0,00:13:55.76,00:13:59.76,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,命に代えても倒すから！》
Dialogue: 0,00:13:59.76,00:14:02.27,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(次郎坊)いまさら何をしても遅い！
Dialogue: 0,00:14:02.27,00:14:04.27,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,圧掌！
Dialogue: 0,00:14:11.29,00:14:13.29,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,ん？
Dialogue: 0,00:14:15.29,00:14:25.30,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:14:29.82,00:14:33.33,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(次郎坊)《な… 何だ？ あれは…》
Dialogue: 0,00:14:33.33,00:14:35.33,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,だが…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:14:35.33,00:14:38.34,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,岩撃！
Dialogue: 0,00:14:38.34,00:14:41.78,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,あっ!?(ﾁｮｳｼﾞ)ムダだ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:14:41.78,00:14:44.29,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,僕は
Dialogue: 0,null,null,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,倍 強い！
Dialogue: 0,00:14:47.29,00:14:49.80,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(次郎坊)うわっ！
Dialogue: 0,00:14:49.80,00:14:52.80,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:14:52.80,00:14:56.81,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ﾁｮｳｼﾞ)食い物の恨みは恐ろしいっていうだろ？
Dialogue: 0,00:14:56.81,00:14:58.81,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,今の一発は
Dialogue: 0,00:14:58.81,00:15:03.32,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,お菓子の最後の一口を食べられた恨みの分だ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:15:03.32,00:15:05.33,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(次郎坊)《バカな… こいつ
Dialogue: 0,00:15:05.33,00:15:08.33,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,体つきが変わるほどのチャクラを…》
Dialogue: 0,00:15:08.33,00:15:10.84,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,そして これは…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:15:10.84,00:15:12.84,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(次郎坊)ぶは～！ ぐっ…！
Dialogue: 0,00:15:12.84,00:15:17.35,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ﾁｮｳｼﾞ)僕のことを捨て駒だ デブだとバカにした分｡
Dialogue: 0,00:15:17.35,00:15:21.86,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,だが 何より 許せないのは…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:15:21.86,00:15:25.87,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(次郎坊)＜バカな隊長を持つと苦労するなぁ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:15:25.87,00:15:27.37,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,下っ端は｡
Dialogue: 0,00:15:27.37,00:15:32.38,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,まぁ 影好きの陰気なヤツの下についてるようなカス連中は
Dialogue: 0,00:15:32.38,00:15:36.39,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,苦労を感じる前に俺が殺してやるがな｡
Dialogue: 0,00:15:36.39,00:15:40.39,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,お前を選んだバカな隊長を恨むんだな＞
Dialogue: 0,00:15:41.83,00:15:45.84,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,僕の親友をバカにしたことだ！
Dialogue: 0,00:15:45.84,00:15:49.85,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,それは どんな高級料理の最後の一口を
Dialogue: 0,00:15:49.85,00:15:51.85,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,横取りされることよりも
Dialogue: 0,00:15:51.85,00:15:56.36,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,デブってバカにされることより…
Dialogue: 0,00:15:56.36,00:15:58.37,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,許せない！
Dialogue: 0,00:15:58.37,00:16:00.37,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(次郎坊)くっ… うっ！
Dialogue: 0,00:16:00.37,00:16:03.88,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ﾁｮｳｼﾞ)《すべてのチャクラを左手へ！》
Dialogue: 0,00:16:03.88,00:16:05.88,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(次郎坊)《ヤ… ヤバい！》
Dialogue: 0,00:16:05.88,00:16:10.39,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ﾁｮｳｼﾞ)この一発は 命より重い‼
Dialogue: 0,00:16:10.39,00:16:13.40,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(次郎坊)ま… 待て！ 早まるな～！
Dialogue: 0,00:16:13.40,00:16:16.40,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,ダァ～～‼
Dialogue: 0,00:16:16.40,00:16:18.91,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(次郎坊)うわ～！
Dialogue: 0,00:16:42.89,00:16:46.40,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,ハァ ハァ ハァ…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:16:46.40,00:16:48.40,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,あっ…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:16:48.40,00:16:50.90,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,あぁ…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:16:53.91,00:16:56.42,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,ハァ ハァ…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:16:56.42,00:16:59.42,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,勝った…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:16:59.42,00:17:02.43,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ﾁｮｳｼﾞ)《この僕が 勝ったんだ…》
Dialogue: 0,00:17:17.96,00:17:23.47,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ﾁｮｳｼﾞ)ハァ ハァ ハァ…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:17:23.47,00:17:26.48,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,あっ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:17:26.48,00:17:28.48,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ﾁｮｳｼﾞ)《みんな…》
Dialogue: 0,00:17:28.48,00:17:32.99,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,ハァ ハァ ハァ…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:17:32.99,00:17:43.00,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:17:52.96,00:18:02.97,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:18:05.49,00:18:10.49,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,ハァ ハァ ハァ…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:18:12.00,00:18:14.00,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ﾁｮｳｻﾞ)＜でもな チョウジ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:18:14.00,00:18:18.01,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,誰よりも お前は優しいヤツだ＞
Dialogue: 0,00:18:20.02,00:18:24.02,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ﾁｮｳｻﾞ)＜いつか お前のそういうところを見てくれる友達が
Dialogue: 0,00:18:24.02,00:18:26.53,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,きっと できる｡
Dialogue: 0,00:18:26.53,00:18:31.54,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,そしたら お前はその友達を何より大切にして
Dialogue: 0,00:18:31.54,00:18:34.55,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,信じ合える仲間になればいい＞
Dialogue: 0,00:18:34.55,00:18:41.99,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ﾁｮｳｼﾞの泣き声)
Dialogue: 0,00:18:41.99,00:18:49.01,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:18:49.01,00:18:52.01,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ﾁｮｳｼﾞ)《｢早く こいってばよ｣｡
Dialogue: 0,00:18:52.01,00:18:55.02,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,ヘヘッ ナルトだな…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:18:55.02,00:18:57.02,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,｢みんな待ってるぜ｣｡
Dialogue: 0,00:18:57.02,00:18:59.53,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,キバ…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:18:59.53,00:19:01.53,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,シカマル…》
Dialogue: 0,00:19:01.53,00:19:11.54,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:19:15.56,00:19:17.57,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(いの)＜猪！＞(ｼｶﾏﾙ)＜鹿！＞
Dialogue: 0,00:19:17.57,00:19:19.07,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜蝶！＞
Dialogue: 0,00:19:19.07,00:19:29.08,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:19:32.60,00:19:37.60,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜ポテチとて 何人たりとも最後の一口は渡さない＞
Dialogue: 0,00:19:39.11,00:19:42.62,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜チョウジとは 長年チーム組んで やってきた｡
Dialogue: 0,00:19:42.62,00:19:45.12,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,俺との連携はいちばん やりやすい＞
Dialogue: 0,00:19:45.12,00:19:52.64,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:19:52.64,00:19:54.64,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ﾁｮｳｼﾞ)《父ちゃん…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:19:54.64,00:19:59.14,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,僕にも…仲間が いっぱいできたよ…》
Dialogue: 0,00:20:01.15,00:20:03.16,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ﾁｮｳｼﾞ)がっ！
Dialogue: 0,00:20:03.16,00:20:13.17,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:20:27.71,00:20:29.71,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,あっ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:20:35.72,00:20:37.72,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,どうした？
Dialogue: 0,00:20:43.17,00:20:45.17,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｼｶﾏﾙ)いや…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:21:41.25,00:21:46.76,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬(ｴﾝﾃﾞｨﾝｸﾞﾃｰﾏ)
